      "span_text": "MDA concentrations in the gastric mucosa were significantly higher in subjects with H. pylori (+) gastritis than in H. pylori (-) subjects and after H. pylori eradication. [CITATION_1] In our study, basal MDA concentrations in H. pylori (+) subjects were markedly higher than those in H. pylori (-) subjects, but the differences did not reach statistical significance (p=0.083).",
